Step 5: Enable Omnichannel Visibility
A unified CRM must consolidate:

Voice calls

Chat sessions

Email threads

Social DMs

Self-service portal interactions

Agents should see a chronological interaction timeline, not fragmented data.

Step 6: Align Workforce Optimization (WFO)
Workforce optimization tools contribute valuable operational insights:

Agent performance trends

Quality management scores

Call handling efficiency

Integrating WFO data enhances both customer and agent experiences.

